reviews.text:
Great service as usual.  My last visit was a year ago and service is still good. I used to visit from time to time years ago when I used to work nearby between 2006 to 2012.

Today, we ordered and my friend was bite late.  They were nice and per my request they provided me a plate to cover the eel that's already served to keep it warm. 

My friend dropped her piece of lotus root on the floor, which she really liked and I asked for an extra piece. They then served extra 2!  

The set is quite big. The beef is so so but definitely worth repeated visits. 

I also have 10% off as I'm the Leonidas VIP. =)
Quiet place for lunch.  Service and food are good.  Will certainly go again.
Spacious seats and quiet atmosphere. Great for dates. Food quality above average and on the pricey side. Great service, polite staff.

Sushi tastes good, sashimi is fresh and of high quality.  Good place for dining with friends or even dining alone.  Price is a not cheap but acceptable.  Lunch sets are of a lower price tag, yet still with good quality and big portion.  As a result it is usually crowded during lunch time.
Very delicious lunch.  Good service.
